---
/**
 * TestimonialsSection.astro
 * Bold, mobile-friendly testimonials with brand styling.
 */
---

<section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 via-white to-red-50 py-20 px-6 md:px-10">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
      <!-- 🔥 Section Header -->
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">
        What <span class="text-red-600">Michigan Homeowners</span> Are Saying
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-14 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Real stories from real customers who got their heat back fast — the Fix My Furnace way.
      </p>
  
      <!-- 💬 Testimonials Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div
          class="flex flex-col items-center bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition"
        >
          <img
            src="/gallery1.jpg"
            alt="Customer portrait"
            class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full object-cover mb-4 ring-4 ring-red-100"
          />
          <p class="text-lg italic text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            “My furnace died on the coldest night of January. Fix My Furnace had a tech at my door in
            under 2 hours — heat was back before midnight. Total lifesavers.”
          </p>
          <div class="text-center">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg">Danielle R.</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Eastpointe, MI</p>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div
          class="flex flex-col items-center bg-red-600 text-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 hover:bg-red-700 transition"
        >
          <img
            src="/gallery2.jpg"
            alt="Customer portrait"
            class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full object-cover mb-4 ring-4 ring-white/40"
          />
          <p class="text-lg italic mb-4 leading-relaxed opacity-95">
            “The techs were polite, clean, and fast. No upselling, no games — just honest work and fair
            pricing. Feels good to hire a Detroit-based crew that cares.”
          </p>
          <div class="text-center">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-white text-lg">Marcus T.</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/80">Dearborn, MI</p>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div
          class="flex flex-col items-center bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition"
        >
          <img
            src="/gallery3.jpg"
            alt="Customer portrait"
            class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full object-cover mb-4 ring-4 ring-red-100"
          />
          <p class="text-lg italic text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            “They replaced my old furnace in one day. Super clean work and even helped me set up my
            thermostat. Highly recommend these guys.”
          </p>
          <div class="text-center">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg">Lorenzo G.</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Detroit, MI</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <!-- 📱 Mobile Scroll Behavior -->
    <style>
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .grid {
          display: flex;
          overflow-x: auto;
          scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
          gap: 1.5rem;
          padding-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .grid > div {
          flex: 0 0 85%;
          scroll-snap-align: center;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </section>
  